        IF failed --> error counter goes up
 
    CALL CHECK-ADDRESS1
        IF failed --> error counter goes up
 
    CALL CHECK-ADDRESS2
        IF failed --> error counter goes up
 
    CALL CHECK-CITY
        IF failed --> error counter goes up
 
    CALL CHECK-STATE
        IF failed --> error counter goes up
 
    CALL CHECK-ZIP
        IF failed --> error counter goes up
 
    CALL CHECK-USERID
        IF failed --> error counter goes up
 
